data.description: Step inside this breathtaking beach cabin on Crystal Beach's Bayside! Recently upgraded both inside and out, this home showcases new flooring, fresh paint, sheetrock, stylish barn doors, and elegant tiles. Get ready to host unforgettable gatherings in the open concept kitchen and living room. The generously-sized primary bedroom offers a cozy retreat, while the renovated primary bath adds a touch of indulgence. After a sun-soaked day at the beach, unwind on the spacious front porch. Situated on not one, but two lots with a fully fenced yard, this property is a true showstopper. And don't forget the added convenience of a generator power inlet box. Don't miss out on this remarkable home!
